Crash Test Program
Author: D. Coderre
Date: 4.10.2015

Brief: Try to debug timing errors by testing simplified code.

Install: 

	 - Install CAEN A2818 or A3818 HW and driver (see caen.it)
	 - Install CAENVMElib (tested with 2.41)
	 - Download this software. 
	 - make

Run:
	- Adjust enum NBoards in main.cc to number of daisy-chained
          V1724 you have in the physical setup
	- make
	- ./sync_test
	- you have to manually fan an S-in to the boards
